OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773418281
OL,3,CEye bank worker wants others to
OL,4,Cconsider cornea donation after his own
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FThe 56-year-old was born with
OL,8,Fcongenital glaucoma, a condition where
OL,9,Fthere is high pressure inside the eye.
OL,10,FHe underwent various surgeries as a
OL,11,Fchild but says he never expected to
OL,12,Fneed a cornea transplant. He has had
OL,13,Fthree, which were all prepared in his
OL,14,Fworkplace.
OL,16,FThis month the NHS celebrates 40 years
OL,17,Fof what went on to become the NHS
OL,18,FBlood and Transplant eye bank.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773418281
OL,3,CEye bank worker wants others to
OL,4,Cconsider cornea donation after his own
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FToni says becoming a recipient himself
OL,8,F"makes me see the work that I do
OL,9,Fdifferently".
OL,11,F"I've always been in awe of the
OL,12,Ffamilies who make that decision to
OL,13,Fdonate their loved one's corneas but I
OL,14,Falso now have that personal experience
OL,15,Fand true understanding of the benefits
OL,16,Fthat a cornea transplant can bring.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773418281
OL,3,CEye bank worker wants others to
OL,4,Cconsider cornea donation after his own
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,F"All of the corneas I received came
OL,8,Fthrough our eye bank - my workplace. I
OL,9,Fdon't think many people could say
OL,10,Fthat! We get a list of what is needed
OL,11,Fand for whom and when I saw my name on
OL,12,Fthere, it was both surreal and
OL,13,Famazing."
OL,15,FWhat later became the NHSBT eye bank
OL,16,Fwas set up in 1986 by the University
OL,17,Fof Bristol's Department of
OL,18,FOphthalmology.
OL,26,@uD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
