SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773418281
OL,3,CEye bank worker wants others to
OL,4,Cconsider cornea donation after his own
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FEye banks had previously been set up
OL,8,Felsewhere in the country, but a lack
OL,9,Fof infrastructure and issues with
OL,10,Fpreserving corneas made it difficult
OL,11,Fto distribute them to other hospitals.
OL,12,FSurgeons outside of these areas had to
OL,13,Frely on local eye donors.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
