OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773418281
OL,3,CEye bank worker wants others to
OL,4,Cconsider cornea donation after his own
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FThe Bristol eye bank team introduced a
OL,8,Fnew method of storing corneas at 34oC,
OL,9,Fthe cornea's normal temperature, which
OL,10,Fincreased the time they could be
OL,11,Fstored from four days to four weeks.
OL,12,FAlongside the introduction of a
OL,13,Fnational distribution service, this
OL,14,Fmeant cornea transplants could become
OL,15,Fan elective procedure, planned well in
OL,16,Fadvance.
OL,26,@pD@dou
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
