OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773418281
OL,3,CEye bank worker wants others to
OL,4,Cconsider cornea donation after his own
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,FNHS Blood and Transplant recorded
OL,8,F4,976 donated corneas in the UK in
OL,9,F2024/25, down from 5,134 in 2023/24.
OL,10,FToni is encouraging people to consider
OL,11,Fcornea donation:
OL,13,FToni says: "The incredible work done
OL,14,Fby the people before me ` and the work
OL,15,Fwe have done since ` has led to people
OL,16,Flike me being able to receive the
OL,17,Ftransplants that we need, when we need
OL,18,Fthem.
OL,26,@uD@LOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
