OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773418281
OL,3,CEye bank worker wants others to
OL,4,Cconsider cornea donation after his own
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,F"But of course, we couldn't do it
OL,8,Fwithout the generosity of the families
OL,9,Fof our donors, who make that decision
OL,10,Fat such a difficult time in their
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,F"I cannot thank the families of my
OL,14,Fdonors enough. It's because of them
OL,15,Fthat I have been able to watch my
OL,16,Fgranddaughter grow up, I can carry on
OL,17,Fwith the activities that I enjoy and
OL,18,Fimportantly, do the work that I do, to
OL,19,Fmake sure that others also receive
OL,20,Fthat precious gift of sight.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1773418281
OL,3,CEye bank worker wants others to
OL,4,Cconsider cornea donation after his own
OL,5,Csurgery
OL,7,F"Please, consider cornea donation and
OL,8,Fregister your decision to donate on
OL,9,Fthe Organ Donor Register. It means
OL,10,Feverything to people like me."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@^O]
